Create Your Pages
Home Tab (Setting Icon) --> New Page --> Standard Page --> +New Blank Page --> content layout : Flexible Layout --> Next
--> Name : About Me --> Create.

Note: At the top of your page, click the main tab (it might now be called About Me)


Home Tab (Setting Icon) --> New Page --> Standard Page --> +New Blank Page --> content layout : Flexible Layout --> Next
--> Name : Experience --> Create.

Home Tab (Setting Icon) --> New Page --> Standard Page --> +New Blank Page --> content layout : Flexible Layout --> Next
--> Name : Education pages --> Create.
