Create Your Navigation

Home Tab (Setting Icon) --> Tile Menu area --> Default Menu : Default Navigation --> Edit Default Navigation
--> Remove (X): Support ,Knowledge --> Add Menu Item -->
Name : About Me
Type : Site Page
Page : About Me (Select curresponding page)
Publicly available (Checked) 

Add Menu Item -->
Name : Experience
Type : Site Page
Page : Experience (Select curresponding page)
Publicly available (Checked) 

Add Menu Item -->
Name : Education
Type : Site Page
Page : Education pages (Select curresponding page)
Publicly available (Checked) --> Save Menu

