Preview and Publish Your Changes
Preview --> 

Note : Test out your page and navigation mappings by clicking each box and seeing that the tab changes to the corresponding tab.
Click the menu items at the top of the page and ensure that the resulting tabs match the menu items.

Back To Builder --> Publish --> Publish --> Got It
